-See what you--

00:13:05.960 --> 00:13:07.340 align:middle line:90%
-Did I even see you?

00:13:07.340 --> 00:13:08.420 align:middle line:90%
-I don't know.

00:13:08.420 --> 00:13:09.200 align:middle line:90%
-Oh.

00:13:09.200 --> 00:13:11.540 align:middle line:90%
