00:13:11.540 --> 00:13:12.080 align:middle line:90%
-Find what?

00:13:12.080 --> 00:13:13.156 align:middle line:90%
-I had the tooth on.

00:13:13.156 --> 00:13:13.655 align:middle line:90%
-Find what?

00:13:13.655 --> 00:13:14.100 align:middle line:90%
Find what?

00:13:14.100 --> 00:13:15.530 align:middle line:84%
-I put it there because
it came out last night.

00:13:15.530 --> 00:13:15.805 align:middle line:90%
-What?

00:13:15.805 --> 00:13:16.080 align:middle line:90%
-Your tooth?

00:13:16.080 --> 00:13:16.335 align:middle line:90%
-Tooth?

00:13:16.335 --> 00:13:17.382 align:middle line:90%
-You're the Tooth Fairy.

00:13:17.382 --> 00:13:18.465 align:middle line:90%
-My teeth didn't come out.

00:13:18.465 --> 00:13:19.321 align:middle line:90%
-I don't know.

00:13:19.321 --> 00:13:21.205 align:middle line:90%
-You look like the Tooth Fairy.

00:13:21.205 --> 00:13:24.960 align:middle line:84%
-What the hell? [CHUCKLES]
Are you serious?

